FBIS4-6884 "dreas079__a94026" FBIS-EAS-94-079-A Daily Report 25 April 1994 ANNEX Mongolia Panel Studies Law on Press, Information Freedom Panel Studies Law on Press, Information Freedom OW2304105694 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1006 GMT 23 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW2304105694 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME English BFN [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 23 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- In accordance with the directive of the president of the country there has been set up a working group for elaborating the draft law on freedom of press and information headed by the Minister of Justice N. Lubsanjab. Included into the composition of the working group are the editors of the largest organs of the press and mass media means. On discussing by the government the draft law should be submitted for consideration by the spring session of the Great State Hural. [sentence as received]
